<p>Apartly, a user can send a private mail to other users using the mail options, this message is not public and can be known to only the sender and receiver. the user can other reply in private or delete the read mails through options.</p><br />
<p>The user can follow the provided terms and conditions by accepting it and register to Baffoons, a free simple social network and use the site with safe privacy of self and others</p>
